# Fleet sync-guard probe sentinels (mcp-rl-fleet). Written transiently into the
# worktree + Mutagen-synced /workspace; the guard unlinks them, but if a build
# races the runner-side unlink the leftover file would change `COPY . .`'s
# checksum every deploy and bust the cached contract/API/web layers (Codex P2,
# 2026-06-02). Gitignored too (`.rl-sync-probe-*`).
.rl-sync-probe-*

